          <figure xmlns:q="http://cnx.rice.edu/qml/1.0" id="import-auto-id1471656"><media id="import-auto-id3184787" alt="The destruction caused by an earthquake in Port-au-Prince, Haiti. Some buildings are shown on two sides of a street. Two buildings are completely destroyed. Rescue people are seen around.">
          <image mime-type="image/png" src="Figure_17_11_01a.jpg" width="375"/>
